@startuml 03 - Muayene Hasta Bilgileri Goruntuleme Sequence

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title UC: Muayene — «include» Hasta Bilgilerinin Görüntülenmesi

actor "Doktor" as DOC
participant "SessionAuthFilter" as FILT
participant "DoktorController" as CTRL
participant "SecurityContextUtil" as SEC
participant "DoctorServiceImpl" as SVC
participant "RandevuRepository" as RREP
participant "HastaMapper" as HMAP

DOC -> FILT : GET /api/doktor/randevu/{randevuId}/hasta\n[Cookie: SESSION_TOKEN=...]

activate FILT
FILT -> FILT : CookieUtil.getCookie(request, "SESSION_TOKEN")
FILT -> FILT : sessionService.getByToken(token)\nsessionService.isValid(session)
FILT -> SEC : set(session.userId, session.userType)
deactivate FILT

FILT -> CTRL : isteği ilet
activate CTRL

CTRL -> SEC : currentUser(Doktor.class)
activate SEC
SEC --> CTRL : Optional<Long> doktorId
deactivate SEC

CTRL -> SVC : getHastaByRandevuId(doktorId, randevuId)
activate SVC

SVC -> RREP : findByIdAndDoktorId(randevuId, doktorId)
activate RREP
note right of RREP
  Yetki kontrolü DB sorgusunda:
  WHERE id = randevuId
    AND doktor_id = doktorId
end note
RREP --> SVC : Optional<Randevu>
deactivate RREP

alt Randevu bulunamadı veya yetki yok
  SVC --> CTRL : EntityNotFoundException
  CTRL --> DOC : 403 / 404
end

SVC -> HMAP : toDTO(randevu.hasta)
activate HMAP
note right of HMAP
  HastaResponseDTO:
  iletişim, boy, kilo
  hastalıklar, randevular
  (her randevuda: tedaviler, reçeteler, raporlar)
end note
HMAP --> SVC : HastaResponseDTO
deactivate HMAP

SVC --> CTRL : HastaResponseDTO
deactivate SVC

CTRL --> DOC : 200 OK\nHastaResponseDTO
deactivate CTRL

@enduml
